    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00003",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "同笑",
      "speakers": [
        "四工匠"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00004",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "数板",
      "speakers": [
        "四工匠"
      ],
      "text": "一生学习铁工匠，全仗五金度时光。昼夜里叮当响，烈火里乌烟扬；造枪刀，铁棍棒，单双剑，丈八枪，铛槊双锤鞭锏铁练流星钩镰枪，九耳连环刀钢叉斧钺两头忙。保管上阵去打仗，建立功勋得胜还乡，功劳簿上把名扬，提写几行，提写几行。",
      "text_length": 108
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00005",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "同笑",
      "speakers": [
        "四工匠"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00006",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "工匠丁"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀呀，诸位长者！我们说的话，自思可笑。用我们打造的兵器，能够疆场厮杀，临阵交锋，还保得胜，这话岂不可笑啊？哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 59
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00007",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "工匠甲"
      ],
      "text": "我们作工的，生活劳累，打造兵器时，说些个吉言吉语，使人家听着，心里高兴，多多赏我们一些酒钱罢啦。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00008",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
