      "speakers": [
        "四工匠"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00009",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "工匠乙"
      ],
      "text": "老哥哥讲的真是心腹言语。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00010",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "工匠丙"
      ],
      "text": "你说得虽好，生在这兵荒马乱之时，纵有金钱，也是无用啊！",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00011",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "工匠丁"
      ],
      "text": "阿叔说的有道理。宁做太平犬，不做乱世人。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00012",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "工匠甲"
      ],
      "text": "闲言少讲。刘、关、张三位找我们打造兵器。闻听这三位义士，要与国家出力报效，大家要尽心尽意地制造。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00013",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "工匠乙",
        "工匠丙",
        "工匠丁"
      ],
      "text": "那是自然。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00014",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "工匠甲"
      ],
      "text": "张家庄去者！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00015",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "工匠乙",
        "工匠丙",
        "工匠丁"
      ],
      "text": "请哪！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00016",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "同梅花板",
      "speakers": [
        "四工匠"
      ],
      "text": "叹苍生乱世，炎汉十常侍误国专权，谋害贤良，生灵涂炭民不安，家家户户少食无穿，连年的荒旱百姓遭难，何时才得个太平年？",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00017",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四工匠同下。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00018",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四青袍同上，同打扫桃园。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00019",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四青袍"
      ],
      "text": "有请诸位义士。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00020",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "苏双",
        "张世平",
        "吕常",
        "方雄"
      ],
      "text": "三位义士请哪！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00021",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备",
        "关羽",
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "诸位义士请！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00022",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "苏双、张世平、吕常、方雄、刘备、关羽、张飞同上。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00023",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "梅花板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "范阳巧遇关与张，心投意合同志向。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00024",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "梅花板",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "为不平把祸闯，逃灾避难走范阳。幸喜得会英雄酒楼上，",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00025",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "梅花板",
      "speakers": [
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "刘关张异姓结拜一炉香。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00026",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "同梅花板",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备",
        "关羽",
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "喜洋洋笑非常，豪杰良将聚一堂。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00027",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "同笑",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备",
        "关羽",
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00028",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖吹打〗。苏双、张世平、吕常、方雄、刘备、关羽、张飞同入席。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00029",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "苏双",
        "张世平",
        "吕常",
        "方雄"
      ],
      "text": "请问关二爷，因何来在范阳，三雄会见？赐教一遍，我们大家洗耳恭听。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00030",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "列位不嫌耳烦，容某下位手舞足蹈，叙说一遍。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00031",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "苏双",
        "张世平",
        "吕常",
        "方雄"
      ],
      "text": "请道其详。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00032",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "平生志气刚，文武记胸膛。恨无出头日，明珠土内藏。宦臣掌朝政，汉室乱纲常，官吏天良丧，黎民遭祸殃。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00033",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "关羽自幼磨穿铁砚，深通诗书。平生好打不平，那日正在酒肆之中沽饮，忽然闯进一白发老者，遍体汗淋，痛哭流涕，惨不忍观。问其情由，老者言道：他名张继昌，乃蒲州解良人氏，老妻去世，只有一女，名叫鸾姣。一日，熊府家人，前来提亲，张家不允。熊祥诈写假借约一张，告到解良苗信台前。想那苗信，乃是熊太守门生，自然是官官相护，将张继昌父女抓到衙中，张鸾姣扣押监中，张继昌用乱棍打下堂来。可怜张继昌年过花甲，上下衙门，叩告喊冤，均不准状。在酒肆之中，遇着关某，领他击鼓鸣冤。狗官又将张继昌暴打，那时某上得堂去，与赃官辩理，问得狗官，哑口无言。狗子熊祥，向某威唬，某家一怒，当堂将熊祥打死。刀劈监牢，放出一伙被难囚犯，救了张氏父女，火焚解良县衙。逃出城来，只听得后面，人声呐喊，官兵追赶而来。那时某身无寸铁，如何抵挡。幸喜路旁，有一圣母娘娘古庙。是某进庙躲藏，不多时间，又听得这哗啦啦一声响亮，火光冲天，乌烟四起！",
      "text_length": 396
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00034",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "四块玉",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "他他他狐群追赶紧，个个凶勇似鹞鹰，那时某独树不成林，手无兵刃无奈古庙把身存，只见那烈焰起，某闯出了火海险境。",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00035",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "那时某从烈火之中，闯出庙门，正遇熊虎，我二人话不投机，被某夺那厮宝剑，斩了熊虎，杀死一伙恶奴。我闯了此祸，山西地面不能存身，因此奔走范阳，巧遇刘、张二位义士。我三人言谈议论，志趣相同，结为金兰之好，又遇众位义士相助，真乃万千之幸！这是关某从解良来到范阳一事。众位义士贻笑了，哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 142
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00036",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "苏双",
        "张世平",
        "吕常",
        "方雄"
      ],
      "text": "关二爷真君子也！我等敬奉三杯。请！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00037",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖牌子〗。苏双、张世平、吕常、方雄、刘备、关羽、张飞同饮酒。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00038",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "苏双",
        "张世平",
        "吕常",
        "方雄"
      ],
      "text": "请问刘兄贵乡何处？有何志向？愿闻其详。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00039",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "备就是这县郡大树楼桑人氏，姓刘名备，字玄德。我乃中山靖王之后，孝景皇帝陛下之玄孙，祖父刘雄，父印刘宠，曾为涿郡太守，去世之后家业贫穷，只落得织席贩履为生。幼读经纶，深通兵法，素怀大志，久欲上报国家，下安黎庶，扫平外患，定国安邦。怎奈我时运不至，唉，真是苍天困煞英雄也！",
      "text_length": 134
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00040",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "叨叨令",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "俺平生怀大志丈夫血性，愧煞我徒有宏图报国心。恨无力斩权臣，外患平，兀的是恼煞人也么哥，兀的是恨煞人也么哥。",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00041",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "苏双",
        "张世平",
        "吕常",
        "方雄"
      ],
      "text": "刘兄乃是汉室宗亲，素怀救国安民之心，令人钦佩！",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00042",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "夸奖了，哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00043",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "列位乡邻！咱张飞家世列位尽知。咱老张的志愿，与关、刘二兄，可算志同道合，相同无二。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00044",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "苏双",
        "张世平",
        "吕常",
        "方雄"
      ],
      "text": "张三爷！我们大家还未曾请教，张三爷你怎么自己就提起来了？",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00045",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "列位义士问完关兄、刘兄，少不得就要问咱老张。咱张飞自己讲了出来，就免得诸位兄台多费唇舌了。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00046",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "苏双",
        "张世平",
        "吕常",
        "方雄"
      ],
      "text": "快人快语，真乃英雄也！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00047",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "咋，咋，咋！哎呀，列位义士抬爱了，哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00048",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小院子上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00049",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小院子"
      ],
      "text": "启禀三位老爷：打造兵器的工匠来了。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00050",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "快快叫他们进来讲话。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00051",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小院子"
      ],
      "text": "有请。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00052",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四工匠"
      ],
      "text": "来了！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00053",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四工匠同上。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00054",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "同念",
      "speakers": [
        "四工匠"
      ],
      "text": "全凭两膀臂力，老君炉内求金。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00055",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四工匠"
      ],
      "text": "参见诸位义士！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00056",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备",
        "关羽",
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "罢了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00057",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四工匠"
      ],
      "text": "请问刘、关、张三位义士，打造兵器，有多少钢铁？",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00058",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备",
        "关羽",
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "折铁两千斤。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00059",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四工匠"
      ],
      "text": "打什么兵器？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00060",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "提龙双股剑。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00061",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "丈八蛇矛枪。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00062",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "三停冷艳锯。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00063",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四工匠"
      ],
      "text": "在哪里打造？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00064",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "家院！领他们去到后园草地打造。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00065",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小院子"
      ],
      "text": "是。诸位随我来。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00066",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小院子、四工匠同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00067",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "苏双",
        "张世平",
        "吕常",
        "方雄"
      ],
      "text": "三位义士！我们必须多聚集些志同之人，前往投军方好。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00068",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备",
        "关羽",
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "那是自然！还须要招军买马。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00069",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小院子上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00070",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小院子"
      ],
      "text": "庄外来了许多壮年汉子，带了许多兵器，良马数十骑，前来拜见刘、关、张与众位义士来了。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00071",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "刘备"
      ],
      "text": "我们何不出庄迎接！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00072",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "苏双",
        "张世平",
        "吕常",
        "方雄",
        "关羽",
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "言得极是！大家一同出庄去者。请！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00073",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00074",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四工匠抬刀、枪、剑同上。刘备、关羽、张飞、苏双、张世平、吕常、方雄同上，观看兵器，称赞。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00075",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "工匠丁"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀！稀奇，稀奇！一阵大风，从草内钻出一条小青蛇，可怜它死在这冷艳锯刀头之上。口内吐出鲜血，真如画在刀头之上，诸位义士请看。",
      "text_length": 62
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00076",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "苏双",
        "张世平",
        "吕常",
        "方雄"
      ],
      "text": "恭喜关兄，贺喜关兄！青龙钻踪冷艳锯刀头之上，口现红光，冷艳锯堪称青龙偃月刀。此乃大吉之兆也！",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00077",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "三笑",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈，哈哈，啊哈哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00078",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "多谢列位义士相赠青龙偃月刀名。关某得志，建功立业，展土辟疆，仰仗诸位金言也！大家收拾马匹，明日一同投军，与国除患，安邦去者！",
      "text_length": 62
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00079",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同尾声",
      "speakers": [
        "苏双",
        "张世平",
        "吕常",
        "方雄",
        "刘备",
        "关羽",
        "张飞"
      ],
      "text": "风云聚会艳阳娇，桃园饮宴集英豪；明日里投军报效，疆场上建立功劳。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70003103_e00080",
      "play_id": "70003103",
      "scene_id": "70003103_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}